These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, police-officer, freelancer
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, grapes, pineapple
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, sudoku, filmmaking, puzzles
 1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 2. the paramedic is the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the paramedic##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the police-officer is on the left of the paramedic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Job    | police-officer   | paramedic       | librarian | freelancer   |
| Food        | banana    | pineapple  | grapes      | apple |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Hobby   | woodworking | sudoku       | filmmaking        | puzzles   |

