.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, photographer, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, juice, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, board-games, filmmaking
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the electrician is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person driving the tram is the photographer##1
4. the bartender is between the person drinking milk and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | electrician | bartender | police-officer | photographer |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice | milk         | lemonade      |
| Hobby         | board-games      | hiking    | filmmaking         | chess   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

