.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, peach, potato
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, russian, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, helicopter, boat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, ice-hockey, volleyball
 1. the russian is the person eating peach##1
 2. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the italian##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the polish##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit | potato  | cauliflower | peach      |
| Nationality   | japanese       | italian    | polish      | russian      |
| Transport           | boat     | subway     | train         | helicopter   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling     | volleyball |

