4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
5. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the videographer is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person playing monopoly##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
