.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, april, june
There 4 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, pineapple, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
House: cape-cod, futuristic, wooden, modern
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the modern house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the futuristic house##1
10. the fan of trance is between the person who's birthday is in october and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | june | october | april     | december       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| House         | wooden  | modern  | cape-cod | futuristic |

