 8. the owner of the rabbit is the entrepreneur##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
