The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, parkour, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 6. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who growsdahlia##2
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking     | puzzles  | magic-tricks |
