 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person driving the van is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Game         | bridge      | snooker | monopoly       | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | documentary | martial-arts | animation |
| Birthday   | december    | march     | may        | june       |
| Transport     | skateboard | motorbike   | helicopter   | van       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, water, milk
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, whist, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, soccer, swimming
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person playing backgammon and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person drinking water is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage          | lemonade | milk   | water   | mirinda |
| Game           | poker   | whist     | backgammon   | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Sport         | skiing    | snowboarding | swimming | soccer    |

 